    {
      "id": "1914750c-f3ba-80c5-98e9-c6b5170ad876",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors use deep learning to predict what should the student’s lext action be based on his past actions. The authors experiment with their approach on two datasetsm one from a higher education institution and the other from a MOOC. ",
